http_bind_host

def http_bind_host(

)-&gt;str:

Address uvicorn binds to (ST_BIND_HOST, default 0.0.0.0).
0.0.0.0 listens on all IPv4 interfaces. Many browsers resolve localhost to IPv6 (::1) first; that does not hit an IPv4-only listener, which often shows as ERR_EMPTY_RESPONSE. Prefer [web_app_url()](https://alix559.github.io/string_therapy/therapy_config.html#web_app_url) in the browser, or set ST_BIND_HOST=:: so localhost works (Linux; 127.0.0.1 may then need the same stack).

