App factory, registry, dock
fast_app supplies rt for route decorators. We register each icon’s HTTP partials, then map slot numbers to callables ([viz](https://alix559.github.io/string_therapy/icon1.html#viz)), not dataclasses. [_dock_icon_ids](https://alix559.github.io/string_therapy/app.html#_dock_icon_ids) filters ST_ICON_IDS / defaults so only implemented slots get buttons—currently 1 and 4.

